    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Capalaba?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Capalaba values are driven by its generous blocks, Capalaba State College, the practical self-contained lifestyle provided by Capalaba Park shopping centre and local services, and consistent demand from families making a deliberate move east for space. The suburb's position as the hub of the eastern residential corridor gives it structural appeal that supports ongoing owner-occupier demand. Properties in quieter residential pockets away from the main commercial corridors attract the strongest family buyer interest.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Capalaba?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Capalaba homes typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb's broad family buyer base and its role as the eastern corridor's service hub mean that genuine buyer interest is consistent throughout the year. Family buyers who have compared the eastern corridor and settled on Capalaba tend to be motivated when the right property appears at a realistic price. Autumn and spring bring the strongest buyer activity, but a well-prepared and correctly priced property will attract competitive interest in any month.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Capalaba?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Capalaba offers a self-contained, family-oriented lifestyle in the eastern corridor, with Capalaba Park shopping centre, Capalaba State College, and Capalaba Regional Park all within easy reach. The suburb's generous residential blocks give families outdoor space that is simply not available at comparable price points closer to the CBD. It is a community built around families, sport clubs, local schools, and the practical day-to-day convenience of having a well-serviced centre close to home.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Capalaba a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Capalaba offers compelling value for families comparing the eastern corridor. The suburb delivers generous blocks, a well-regarded Prep to Year 12 school option, extensive local amenity, and an established owner-occupier community at a price point that reflects its location rather than any shortcoming in what it offers. Consistent demand from families making a deliberate move east for space and school options has supported the market, and the suburb's role as the hub of its corridor gives it ongoing structural appeal.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

